PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME FROM CONTENTTYPES CONTENTTYPES WHERE ((SELECT COUNT(PSX_AUTOTRANSLATION.LOCALE) FROM PSX_AUTOTRANSLATION WHERE PSX_AUTOTRANSLATION.CONTENTTYPEID = CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID) < (SELECT COUNT(LOCALEID) FROM RXLOCALE WHERE STATUS=1)) ORDER BY CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME ASC
